{"tid":1322991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【最新片段還原真相】青年遭警施酷刑插眼在先 涉咬警手指自衞(片)","createTime":"2019-07-16T06:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T22:05:38.000Z","uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fca6104fef1e60e4c8ee1cd6de131c19532ff24c","tid":1322991,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:03:44.000Z","msg":"【最新片段還原真相】青年遭警施酷刑插眼在先 涉咬警手指自衞<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/vdo/20190716/720pix/1563254338_bf1d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2Fvdo%2F20190716%2F720pix%2F1563254338_bf1d.png&h=9b04a142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n克警前晚（14日）疑罔顧沙田多個商場的顧客、途人、同袍和抗爭者的安全，圍堵和包抄正在離開的抗爭者，更一度堵塞港鐵站閘口，在人流極密集、不少一家大細聚腳的新城市廣場，與抗爭者「困獸鬥」混戰。《蘋果》收到市民拍攝的片段，比對USP社媒拍攝的照片，發現有警察捉住商場內一名年輕男子時，用手指插入青年的右眼，施以酷刑，青年於是涉用口咬住該名警察的手指自衞。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190716/59828939\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190716%2F59828939&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=e48092a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190716%2F59828939&h=ca1c1427\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190716/59828939</a>(片)"},{"pid":"0b8bcb07d3c5af543fc3aa09abbb4bfb791f2904","tid":1322991,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69cede03a24291f4e11a67b40263cf519159dae3","tid":1322991,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:05:26.000Z","msg":"pUSH"},{"pid":"cd455f3fd174a84bdbe215dfb69f46619815b421","tid":1322991,"uid":44701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:07:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"36750d176b56a2baee967bd2798c4f06f0184d35","tid":1322991,"uid":44701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:07:52.000Z","msg":"Push ah"},{"pid":"f6d6f36a3da33b7a025682b60973d232b367ee8b","tid":1322991,"uid":256014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T22:05:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">　　示威者</span><span style=\"color: red;\">十分有牙力</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">（講嘢</span><span style=\"color: red;\">最緊要有牙力），</span><span style=\"color: green;\">我</span><span style=\"color: red;\">比較關注</span><span style=\"color: green;\">法官</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">怎樣判？</span><span style=\"color: green;\">傳媒</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">要</span><span style=\"color: red;\">緊貼</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">報導，</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">　　還有，</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">另</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">一個</span><span style=\"color: green;\">示威者</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">於</span><span style=\"color: green;\">沙田新城市廣場</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">已經</span>被<span style=\"color: green;\">警察</span>扯爛<span style=\"color: purple;\">衣服</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">與及</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">制服，</span><span style=\"color: green;\">傳媒</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">報導</span><span style=\"color: green;\">他</span>被帶到<span style=\"color: green;\">葵涌警署</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">後，</span><span style=\"color: green;\">他</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">於</span><span style=\"color: green;\">警署</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">內</span>襲擊<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">３名</span><span style=\"color: green;\">警察，</span>匪夷所思（越來越似<span style=\"color: green;\">國內公安），</span><span style=\"color: green;\">警署</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">是</span><span style=\"color: green;\">警察</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">的</span><span style=\"color: green;\">主場，</span><span style=\"color: red;\">一打三，唔講得笑，</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">看看</span><span style=\"color: green;\">傳媒</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">之後</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">怎樣</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">報導。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">　　最後，</span>罪魁禍首<span style=\"color: blue;\">是</span><span style=\"color: green;\">林鄭月娥</span>條死八婆。<br />\n</strong></span>"}]}